The allocation shall be calculated as follows:
For each of fiscal years 2011 through 2016............$6.75 per each resident of the area served;
For fiscal year 2017............$7.00 per each resident of the area served;
For fiscal year 2018............$7.25 per each resident of the area served; and
For fiscal year 2019 and each fiscal year thereafter............$7.50 per each resident of the area served.

The allocation shall be calculated as follows:
For each of fiscal years 2010 through 2016............$1.67 per State resident;
For fiscal year 2017............$1.73 per State resident;
For fiscal year 2018............$1.79 per State resident; and
For fiscal year 2019 and each fiscal year thereafter............$1.85 per State resident.
